{"tid":1725281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動po]咪再屌大學","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T19:22:57.000Z","uid":82920,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de746aaa25853e4bc73ff7ebf0ffbd94c7f97562","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:48:30.000Z","msg":"呢幾日抗爭重點好似放左係大學據點<br />\n應唔應該守，有乜作用等<br />\n然後內哄=運動停滯<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放返重點係政權！</span></span><br />\n同<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">義士死亡失蹤受傷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有據點一定有鬼有督灰撚<br />\n請大家唔好再拗<br />\n做實事<br />\n嘗試達成共識<br />\n無共識就<br />\n要守就守，留就留<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">守既人唔洗多勇武</span><br />\n咁勇武做唔會無用武之地<br />\n可以繼續係<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">出面開花</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nhall area成為<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">物資安全屋</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而唔係話死守<br />\n(當然睇場人數同rb要做得好)<br />\n守門口亦要謹慎<br />\n確保，有足夠既本校人守住<br />\n否則好似cu咁被搶陣地（無乜cu人）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">危險唔夠人就真係要撤</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反而敵方商議或改變政策中<br />\n我方就要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">順水推舟</span></span><br />\n係大家接受火攻下<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再將武力/行動升級</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">務求政府回應<br />\n先係重點</span><br />\n否則只是處於被動一方<br />\n繼續比狗撚返轉頭<br />\n然後被自殺被捕<br />\n只會係我方受損<br />\n<br />\n民意，其實早已歸邊<br />\n係反既都會繼續反(叻哥理論)<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">做事唔應該再以民意為先<br />\n而係對準政權</span></span><br />\n我地再無咁多時間去令香港人承受打仗般既世界<br />\n必須食住時間<br />\n令經濟，外資受損<br />\n同再搵下政府最重要春袋(可討論，未知)<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理非出場，勇武先可以出場</span></span><br />\n因為佢地代價係一出捉到就坐<br />\n而和理非捉到通常告唔入<br />\n所以之後既活動都請和理非大量進入一<br />\n而如果<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中環西裝友真係想支持我地</span></span>，請唔好lunch time先黎，我想信你地可以做得更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">都唔想你地無故被捕</span><br />\n大家，和理塞可以繼續，但對方會轉陣，終有一日大家都要跟住一轉<br />\n<br />\n以上愚見，請開方討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d71d92799331495315ce85f3be9c21b3101bd7","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:49:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db94688a6b28cfc13a961a77d9ee192ceb03652","tid":1725281,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:52:31.000Z","msg":"入嚟睇一睇<br />\n<br />\n唔該想知中大發生咩事就入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725278</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"869f22a0fab72dadf4471157b05bd9eaadf1f46c","tid":1725281,"uid":251397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"各位中大生，唔知幫唔到大家<br />\n<br />\n呢條片係一位科學教授講述催淚彈嘅嚴重性<br />\n<br />\n中大釋放左咁多催淚彈，環境已經係極度污染<br />\n<br />\n有些同學睡在運動場，很危險，因為就算沒有味道，有毒化學物質在空氣裏充斥着，快則可以見到皮膚紅腫，慢則幾十年後出現癌症。<br />\n<br />\n我在此擔心各位中大人的安危，請大家考慮撤離或不撤離。 <br />\n<br />\n催淚彈害人不淺，禍及環境，禍及下一代！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/179179469403545/posts/453229281998561?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F179179469403545%2Fposts%2F453229281998561%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=77341c66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/179179469403545/posts/453229281998561?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"1bb1d82c16f2116012751670ab50fe57ec57baca","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:11:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c47f5600be58fdd6ff3a147f742305b5d73f1b","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:12:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />是"},{"pid":"6596ab17328385ad3cb533e92367775bbf0f1821","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0e9a05eb6bc8ed073508bcd747c093fe6e2de1","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d04359874d32e08af9dd9161b9fe3b581962be","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:13:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4364279673a8d7c4574a7d07ce6c50a642034889","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:13:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336ff60c30b0227498f50a4c7ae5cdac3d80f785","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45476a695c92c29762c9139d7343edc8d4f92b18","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d2a23e769143b71cf717a08d955a116c46406e","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T19:20:16.000Z","msg":"推🤡"},{"pid":"565996b7baa1e44cafcba11eef989ff8fc03c35c","tid":1725281,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20